amateur night is a 2016 american comedy film written and directed by lisa addario and joe syracuse .   their early experiences in hollywood were the basis for the plot of the film .   the film stars jason biggs , jenny mollen , janet montgomery , ashley tisdale and eddie murphy 's daughter bria murphy ( in her film debut ) .   amateur night held its world premiere in los angeles on july 25 , 2016 , and was theatrically released in the united states on august 5 , 2016 , by cinedigm .   the film was met with mixed reviews from critics .